90
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:02,720
Mr. Xu.

91
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:07,960
Well, earlier,

92
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:09,039
a friend in the industry

93
00:13:09,039 --> 00:13:10,360
