as direction for our rebuttal.

97
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:18,279
Go on.

98
00:13:19,039 --> 00:13:20,799
The first direction is plot-wise.

99
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:22,080
Like

100
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:24,279
what I wrote in chapter ten,

101
00:13:24,559 --> 00:13:26,000
the scenes between the male lead

102
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:26,840
and some side characters.

103
00:13:27,879 --> 00:13:29,399
The fried chicken scene.

104
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:34,919
I'm in.

105
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,919
Bring a ladder after school

106
00:13:38,519 --> 00:13:39,679
