121
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:03,039
[Oh no.]

122
00:14:03,279 --> 00:14:04,759
[With my dad's temper,]

123
00:14:04,919 --> 00:14:06,039
[Xu Huaisong is done for.]

124
00:14:06,799 --> 00:14:08,559
[No, I need to figure something out.]

125
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:09,720
Are you going or not?

126
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,240
Thank you, Madam.

127
00:14:12,919 --> 00:14:13,480
When I'm done with it,

128
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:14,679
I'll return it right away.

129
00:14:14,679 --> 00:14:15,960
No rush. Tell Mr. Ruan he's welcome

130
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:16,919
