Just bring it back

131
00:14:17,399 --> 00:14:18,399
- whenever you have time.
- I've got it.

132
00:14:19,039 --> 00:14:19,840
Thank you.

133
00:14:34,679 --> 00:14:35,519
Xu Huaisong.

134
00:14:36,519 --> 00:14:37,159
Now they won't

135
00:14:37,159 --> 00:14:38,320
