147
00:15:10,919 --> 00:15:12,159
I wanna reflect her feelings of secret love.

148
00:15:12,559 --> 00:15:13,480
But for The Poet,

149
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:14,519
it's from the male lead's perspective,

150
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:15,600
followed by

151
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:16,720
