175
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:42,559
If so,

176
00:16:42,879 --> 00:16:43,919
I can take a look now.

177
00:16:44,039 --> 00:16:44,679
No, no.

178
00:16:45,080 --> 00:16:46,399
It's all trivial stuff.

179
00:16:46,399 --> 00:16:47,559
Nothing important.

180
00:16:48,519 --> 00:16:49,159
Let's continue.

181
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:51,519
Where were we?

182
00:16:52,799 --> 00:16:54,120
When I returned the ladder...

183
00:16:58,639 --> 00:16:59,440
No.

184
00:16:59,799 --> 00:17:01,799
