with our case, does it?

192
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:17,759
Ms. Ruan,

193
00:17:18,839 --> 00:17:20,119
in order to reach a resolution

194
00:17:20,119 --> 00:17:21,720
that satisfies both of us,

195
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:23,039
