200
00:17:34,440 --> 00:17:35,000
So…

201
00:17:35,720 --> 00:17:37,720
What does whether the female lead

202
00:17:38,559 --> 00:17:39,319
was punished

203
00:17:39,319 --> 00:17:40,640
