224
00:18:36,119 --> 00:18:37,599
Even though he's aloof,

225
00:18:38,359 --> 00:18:40,240
he's gentle at heart,

226
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:44,759
and a well-rounded top student.

227
00:19:04,279 --> 00:19:04,880
Huaisong.

228
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:08,039
I reread Senior

229
00:19:08,039 --> 00:19:09,079
Ruan Yu's novel,

230
00:19:09,880 --> 00:19:11,000
