240
00:19:33,240 --> 00:19:34,519
Did your homework not keep you busy enough?

241
00:19:46,599 --> 00:19:49,000
But the male lead

242
00:19:50,240 --> 00:19:51,680
in The Poet's novel...

243
00:19:53,440 --> 00:19:55,880
If my male lead's demeanor

244
00:19:56,279 --> 00:19:57,640
is more like

245
00:19:57,839 --> 00:19:59,359
Hanazawa Rui

246
00:19:59,799 --> 00:20:00,680
from Meteor Garden,

247
00:20:01,720 --> 00:20:03,599
then The Poet's male lead

248
00:20:04,559 --> 00:20:05,839
is more like

249
00:20:07,599 --> 00:20:09,039
Domyoji Tsukasa

250
00:20:09,039 --> 00:20:09,920
from Meteor Garden.

251
00:20:23,119 --> 00:20:23,880
Don't touch it.

252
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:25,039
This is for Ruan Yu.

253
00:20:25,279 --> 00:20:26,319
Ruan Yu?

254
00:20:26,319 --> 00:20:27,000
Again?
This is for her too?

255
00:20:28,359 --> 00:20:29,519
You're always giving her gifts.

256
00:20:30,440 --> 00:20:31,200
You bet.

257
00:20:35,400 --> 00:20:36,000
Girl.

258
00:20:36,640 --> 00:20:37,640
I saw your favorite grilled corn

259
00:20:37,640 --> 00:20:39,039
