262
00:20:43,599 --> 00:20:44,400
It's you again.

263
00:20:44,640 --> 00:20:46,160
So what if you're "Class 10's Domyoji"?

264
00:20:46,440 --> 00:20:47,000
Who do you think you are,

265
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:48,240
