266
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:49,598
So childish.

267
00:20:49,599 --> 00:20:51,359
So childish.

268
00:20:51,359 --> 00:20:52,319
What are you guys looking at?

269
00:20:53,319 --> 00:20:53,839
Don't you know Ruan Yu
is the one I've set my sights on?

270
00:20:59,839 --> 00:21:00,440
I'm already being nice

271
00:21:00,440 --> 00:21:01,599
