273
00:21:03,200 --> 00:21:04,920
If you keep pestering me

274
00:21:04,920 --> 00:21:06,119
and interrupting my studies,

275
00:21:06,119 --> 00:21:06,559
we'll

276
00:21:06,559 --> 00:21:08,119
