277
00:21:09,039 --> 00:21:09,839
Ruan Yu, Ruan Yu.

278
00:21:10,240 --> 00:21:10,720
Ruan Yu.

279
00:21:13,119 --> 00:21:13,759
And one more thing,

280
00:21:14,599 --> 00:21:15,720
