284
00:21:32,400 --> 00:21:33,640
I might have made it too complicated.

285
00:21:34,039 --> 00:21:35,519
To sum it up simply,

286
00:21:35,839 --> 00:21:37,240
I think The Poet's male lead

287
00:21:37,240 --> 00:21:38,480
is very playful and childish.

288
00:21:39,640 --> 00:21:41,039
Aren't most boys that age

289
00:21:41,599 --> 00:21:42,599
pretty much the same?

290
00:21:43,960 --> 00:21:44,720
How are they the same?

291
00:21:44,720 --> 00:21:45,880
How can they be the same?

292
00:21:46,519 --> 00:21:47,440
The Poet's male lead

293
00:21:47,440 --> 00:21:48,920
is so different from mine.

294
00:21:49,400 --> 00:21:50,079
Look at him, going to great lengths
for fried chicken and soda

295
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:51,880
all the time.

296
00:21:52,559 --> 00:21:53,720
Isn't that playful?

297
00:21:55,759 --> 00:21:56,559
And to win the female lead's favor,
he puts on an act

298
00:21:57,559 --> 00:21:58,640
in front of her

299
00:21:58,640 --> 00:21:59,359
every single day.

300
00:21:59,440 --> 00:22:00,440
Isn't that childish?

301
00:22:00,920 --> 00:22:01,720
That's nothing like my male lead,
not at all.

302
00:22:03,279 --> 00:22:03,720
I remember there are

303
00:22:03,720 --> 00:22:04,920
more scenes to prove it.

304
00:22:05,039 --> 00:22:06,279
Wait, let me show you.

305
00:22:06,279 --> 00:22:07,039
No need.

306
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,319
That's it for today's meeting.

307
00:22:09,880 --> 00:22:10,720
We'll continue another day.

308
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:21,759
He just hung up like that?

309
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:27,559
Why does he seem kind of upset?

310
00:22:30,559 --> 00:22:32,039
I wasn't talking about him.

311
00:22:50,799 --> 00:22:52,200
[Daydreaming, buddy?]

312
00:22:52,559 --> 00:22:53,599
[Asking a question like that]

313
00:22:54,000 --> 00:22:55,200
[guarantees you'll never]

314
00:22:55,200 --> 00:22:56,559
[be an aloof man in this lifetime.]

315
00:22:57,160 --> 00:22:58,680
[Aloof, elegant,]

316
00:22:58,880 --> 00:23:00,279
[and always confident.]

317
00:23:25,799 --> 00:23:26,920
How to be aloof?

318
00:23:39,079 --> 00:23:39,640
[Something's off.]

319
00:23:41,640 --> 00:23:42,640
[Very off.]

320
00:23:50,559 --> 00:23:52,400
Lawyer Xu, are you asleep?

321
00:24:11,200 --> 00:24:12,119
Nothing urgent.

322
00:24:12,680 --> 00:24:13,920
I just wanted to ask,

323
00:24:14,480 --> 00:24:15,640
during today's meeting,

324
00:24:15,960 --> 00:24:17,359
did I say something wrong?

325
00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:19,160
Why did you suddenly

326
00:24:19,759 --> 00:24:20,599
hang up the video call?

327
00:24:34,960 --> 00:24:35,480
You didn't.

328
00:24:36,079 --> 00:24:37,680
I received an urgent work assignment.

329
00:24:40,880 --> 00:24:42,079
But Ms. Ruan,

330
00:24:42,599 --> 00:24:43,400
you harshly criticized

331
00:24:43,400 --> 00:24:44,640
the other male lead

332
00:24:44,799 --> 00:24:46,200
with strong personal feelings.

333
00:24:46,799 --> 00:24:47,720
You were in a subjective

334
00:24:47,720 --> 00:24:48,839
and irrational state, so we should

335
00:24:49,240 --> 00:24:50,400
postpone discussing the case.

336
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:53,079
I see.

337
00:24:54,640 --> 00:24:55,920
That's too strict.

338
00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:03,359
Lawyer Xu, you misunderstood me.

339
00:25:04,000 --> 00:25:05,079
I was just

340
00:25:05,240 --> 00:25:06,079
a bit anxious

341
00:25:06,079 --> 00:25:07,319
because you didn't see the difference

342
00:25:07,599 --> 00:25:08,440
between the two male leads.

343
00:25:24,039 --> 00:25:24,599
I do see it.

344
00:25:32,599 --> 00:25:34,400
[She doesn't like me at all.]

345
00:25:36,920 --> 00:25:38,240
[How can I confess my feelings?]

346
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:48,559
Elite lawyers are different, huh?

347
00:25:48,559 --> 00:25:49,240
Always have to stay

348
00:25:49,240 --> 00:25:50,680
objective and rational.

349
00:25:51,359 --> 00:25:52,279
Did he schedule

350
00:25:52,279 --> 00:25:53,519
the next meeting with you?

351
00:25:55,359 --> 00:25:55,880
No.

352
00:25:56,839 --> 00:25:57,400
Hopefully he's

353
00:25:57,400 --> 00:25:58,759
tied up with some big case

354
00:25:59,279 --> 00:26:00,200
and doesn't have much time

355
00:26:00,200 --> 00:26:01,440
for another video meeting with me.

356
00:26:01,920 --> 00:26:03,000
It feels like

357
00:26:03,000 --> 00:26:04,200
I'm back in school taking an exam.

358
00:26:07,599 --> 00:26:08,599
That's not impossible.

359
00:26:08,680 --> 00:26:09,920
I looked him up.

360
00:26:10,279 --> 00:26:11,200
The SG copyright case
he handled in the US

361
00:26:12,160 --> 00:26:14,599
set foreign media ablaze back then.

362
00:26:14,759 --> 00:26:17,200
They said the young and promising

363
00:26:17,200 --> 00:26:18,480
Lawyer Xu, single-handedly,

364
00:26:18,480 --> 00:26:20,279
brought SG back from the brink.

365
00:26:21,319 --> 00:26:21,960
Word is,

366
00:26:21,960 --> 00:26:23,519
what SG pays him now

367
00:26:23,519 --> 00:26:24,880
as legal counsel

368
00:26:24,880 --> 00:26:26,079
is enough to set him up

369
00:26:26,079 --> 00:26:27,240
for the rest of his life.

370
00:26:28,519 --> 00:26:29,200
That impressive?

371
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:31,599
Makes my years of
crushing on him worth it.

372
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:34,000
Proves

373
00:26:34,279 --> 00:26:35,440
I've got pretty good taste.

374
00:26:35,839 --> 00:26:37,680
Good taste alone won't cut it.

375
00:26:37,960 --> 00:26:39,000
He's so sharp,

376
00:26:39,640 --> 00:26:41,119
are you sure you haven't slipped up?

377
00:26:44,559 --> 00:26:45,599
Thanks, miss.

378
00:26:45,599 --> 00:26:46,480
I'll try it on myself.

379
00:26:46,759 --> 00:26:47,240
Okay.

380
00:26:51,920 --> 00:26:52,759
Not yet.

381
00:26:53,920 --> 00:26:54,680
You know what,

382
00:26:54,920 --> 00:26:55,880
to not expose myself,

383
00:26:55,880 --> 00:26:57,000
I have to outwit him every day,

384
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:57,720
it's exhausting.

385
00:26:58,319 --> 00:26:59,000
One video call

386
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:00,240
feels like I've run 800 meters.

387
00:27:02,000 --> 00:27:03,240
But after all these years,

388
00:27:04,480 --> 00:27:05,599
he hasn't changed much.

389
00:27:07,079 --> 00:27:08,839
I can hear a hint of

390
00:27:08,839 --> 00:27:10,880
lingering affection.

391
00:27:14,480 --> 00:27:15,400
No way.

392
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:18,960
How is there not?

393
00:27:19,440 --> 00:27:20,519
Look at you every time

394
00:27:20,519 --> 00:27:21,960
you mention Xu Huaisong,

395
00:27:21,960 --> 00:27:23,200
your emotions fluctuate

396
00:27:23,200 --> 00:27:24,519
just like when you were eighteen.

397
00:27:27,480 --> 00:27:29,200
Who wouldn't get emotional

398
00:27:29,200 --> 00:27:30,519
over something this absurd?

399
00:27:31,880 --> 00:27:32,680
Besides,

400
00:27:32,920 --> 00:27:34,240
love at twenty-eight

401
00:27:34,640 --> 00:27:36,079
can't be like it was at eighteen,

402
00:27:36,559 --> 00:27:38,119
where hormonal urges were enough.

403
00:27:39,160 --> 00:27:40,319
It's not just about charm and

404
00:27:40,319 --> 00:27:41,319
physical attraction,

405
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:43,480
but also personality in daily interaction,

406
00:27:44,119 --> 00:27:45,640
aligned values mentally,

407
00:27:45,920 --> 00:27:47,039
and a spiritual connection.

408
00:27:47,759 --> 00:27:48,759
These four conditions

409
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:49,920
are all indispensable.

410
00:27:51,920 --> 00:27:53,440
My little emotional outburst

411
00:27:54,279 --> 00:27:55,799
is far from a rekindled flame.

412
00:27:56,680 --> 00:27:57,960
At most,

413
00:27:59,359 --> 00:28:00,759
it's just nostalgia for youth,

414
00:28:02,119 --> 00:28:03,279
a fond remembrance

415
00:28:04,319 --> 00:28:05,759
of the self I was back then.

416
00:28:06,480 --> 00:28:07,960
No wonder you're a writer.

417
00:28:08,759 --> 00:28:10,319
Four conditions,

418
00:28:10,319 --> 00:28:11,920
and nostalgia and remembrance?

419
00:28:12,519 --> 00:28:13,839
You draw the line so clearly.

420
00:28:14,960 --> 00:28:15,680
But still, he was someone

421
00:28:15,680 --> 00:28:17,200
you had such a huge crush on back then.

422
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:20,319
You should feel a bit familiar, at least?

423
00:28:23,079 --> 00:28:23,960
Here I am,

424
00:28:23,960 --> 00:28:25,119
holding onto my disguise for dear life.

425
00:28:25,119 --> 00:28:25,759
How could I possibly

426
00:28:25,759 --> 00:28:26,960
feel any closeness to him?

427
00:28:28,039 --> 00:28:28,759
Besides,

428
00:28:29,160 --> 00:28:30,599
it's been ten years.

429
00:28:31,200 --> 00:28:32,440
Now, I only see him as

430
00:28:32,759 --> 00:28:33,319
a responsible,

431
00:28:33,319 --> 00:28:34,839
competent lawyer.

432
00:28:35,319 --> 00:28:36,519
He'd better not be so responsible.

433
00:28:36,839 --> 00:28:37,839
It'd be best if he hands

434
00:28:37,839 --> 00:28:38,920
my case to Lawyer Liu.

435
00:28:40,200 --> 00:28:41,079
What about Lawyer Liu?

436
00:28:41,559 --> 00:28:43,240
You've worked with him for a few days.

437
00:28:43,480 --> 00:28:45,599
Did sparks of love

438
00:28:45,599 --> 00:28:47,400
ignite between you two?

439
00:28:49,480 --> 00:28:50,680
Forget it, with my current situation,

440
00:28:50,680 --> 00:28:51,759
I have no mood for love.

441
00:28:51,759 --> 00:28:53,039
Even if I wanted to fall in love,

442
00:28:53,359 --> 00:28:54,000
Lawyer Liu isn't

443
00:28:54,000 --> 00:28:55,079
my type at all.

444
00:28:55,640 --> 00:28:56,519
How do you know

445
00:28:56,519 --> 00:28:57,839
if you don't try?

446
00:28:58,240 --> 00:28:59,160
Look at me and Zhang Chuan,
when we first got together,

447
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:00,720
I couldn't stand him.

448
00:29:00,920 --> 00:29:01,839
But look how it turned out.

449
00:29:03,559 --> 00:29:04,359
So good.

450
00:29:05,720 --> 00:29:06,480
It does smell nice.

451
00:29:07,400 --> 00:29:08,000
Hi. Can I get

452
00:29:08,279 --> 00:29:09,400
a bottle of this perfume, please?

453
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:09,920
Sure.

454
00:29:17,319 --> 00:29:18,000
What's wrong?

455
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:20,640
I feel like someone's watching us.

456
00:29:20,880 --> 00:29:21,519
It's weird.

457
00:29:22,359 --> 00:29:23,440
It's broad daylight.

458
00:29:23,799 --> 00:29:24,960
Are you switching from romance

459
00:29:24,960 --> 00:29:26,200
to horror?

460
00:29:27,160 --> 00:29:27,960
Just pick your perfume.

461
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:29,359
Which one?

462
00:29:29,359 --> 00:29:30,640
- This one.
- Senior Ruan.

463
00:29:31,920 --> 00:29:32,960
It's really you.

464
00:29:45,480 --> 00:29:46,480
Excuse me, who are you?

465
00:29:47,680 --> 00:29:49,240
I'm Cen Sisi!

466
00:29:49,319 --> 00:29:50,519
Don't you remember me?

467
00:30:01,200 --> 00:30:02,440
Oh my gosh.

468
00:30:02,759 --> 00:30:04,640
I haven't seen you in ages!

469
00:30:04,960 --> 00:30:05,799
I was just over there
peeking at you for ages. I was afraid

470
00:30:06,680 --> 00:30:08,079
I'd mistaken you for someone else.

471
00:30:09,119 --> 00:30:09,880
Did you end up staying

472
00:30:09,880 --> 00:30:11,119
in Hang City after graduation?

473
00:30:13,200 --> 00:30:14,119
This is our college junior,
Cen Sisi.

474
00:30:15,119 --> 00:30:16,240
She was in the Chinese department too.

475
00:30:16,880 --> 00:30:18,599
This is my best friend, Shen Mingying.

476
00:30:18,599 --> 00:30:19,079
Nice to meet you.

477
00:30:19,400 --> 00:30:20,279
You too.

478
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:23,039
I remember now.

479
00:30:23,440 --> 00:30:25,079
Back then, you two were

480
00:30:25,079 --> 00:30:26,400
both in the Arts Department with Shican,

481
00:30:26,400 --> 00:30:27,039
right?

482
00:30:30,279 --> 00:30:31,880
Shican and I grew up together.

483
00:30:32,000 --> 00:30:33,240
I saw you so many times

484
00:30:33,240 --> 00:30:34,720
when I went to visit him.

485
00:30:35,559 --> 00:30:36,880
Seeing you three spend all day

486
00:30:36,880 --> 00:30:38,079
in the Arts Department,

487
00:30:38,319 --> 00:30:39,000
those were good times.

488
00:30:40,279 --> 00:30:40,759
Oh, right!

489
00:30:41,039 --> 00:30:42,119
He's got a performance

490
00:30:42,119 --> 00:30:43,039
in Hang City in a few days.

491
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:44,799
Did you make plans to meet up?

492
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:47,759
We don't keep in touch much now.

493
00:30:48,200 --> 00:30:49,519
I didn't even know he was coming.

494
00:30:51,319 --> 00:30:52,079
Yeah, that's true.

495
00:30:52,079 --> 00:30:53,880
After he returned to China last year,

496
00:30:53,880 --> 00:30:54,920
he's been really busy.

497
00:30:55,240 --> 00:30:55,960
Even his family

498
00:30:55,960 --> 00:30:57,240
hardly gets to see him.

499
00:30:57,920 --> 00:30:59,160
But no matter how busy he is,

500
00:30:59,279 --> 00:31:00,319
he shouldn't forget his old friends,

501
00:31:00,319 --> 00:31:00,839
right?

502
00:31:01,640 --> 00:31:02,160
How about this.

503
00:31:02,799 --> 00:31:03,880
I'll arrange a time with him

504
00:31:03,880 --> 00:31:05,000
and we can all get together.

505
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:06,640
That okay?

506
00:31:10,359 --> 00:31:11,200
Senior.

507
00:31:11,519 --> 00:31:13,279
What do you do for a living now?

508
00:31:14,160 --> 00:31:15,400
I'm kind of a freelancer.

509
00:31:17,599 --> 00:31:19,000
Don't tell me you're a writer.

510
00:31:21,680 --> 00:31:22,440
Not really.

511
00:31:22,880 --> 00:31:24,000
Just an average online writer.

512
00:31:24,359 --> 00:31:24,839
And you?

513
00:31:25,119 --> 00:31:26,839
What job did you get after graduation?

514
00:31:27,960 --> 00:31:28,880
Me?

515
00:31:29,799 --> 00:31:30,799
I just work

516
00:31:30,799 --> 00:31:32,519
at my family's company.

517
00:31:34,759 --> 00:31:35,640
But our school

518
00:31:35,640 --> 00:31:37,000
really produces talented people.

519
00:31:37,440 --> 00:31:39,079
Look at Shican, a big star.

520
00:31:39,079 --> 00:31:40,799
And you, a renowned writer.

521
00:31:41,319 --> 00:31:43,119
I do know a few

522
00:31:43,119 --> 00:31:44,160
online writers.

523
00:31:44,799 --> 00:31:45,920
This circle

524
00:31:45,920 --> 00:31:46,920
seems really tough.

525
00:31:47,720 --> 00:31:49,119
They really have it hard.

526
00:31:49,799 --> 00:31:50,599
I'm okay.

527
00:31:50,960 --> 00:31:51,799
I'm pretty laid-back.

528
00:31:52,079 --> 00:31:53,240
I just write for fun.

529
00:31:54,480 --> 00:31:56,519
Yeah, the online environment

530
00:31:56,519 --> 00:31:57,400
isn't great right now.

531
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:59,799
It's good you can stay positive.

532
00:32:09,640 --> 00:32:10,799
Sorry, I need to take this.

533
00:32:11,160 --> 00:32:12,480
Yeah, go ahead.

534
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:18,000
Mr. Xu.
Just got

535
00:32:18,799 --> 00:32:19,839
news from the court.

536
00:32:20,319 --> 00:32:21,200
The case has advanced

537
00:32:21,200 --> 00:32:22,559
to the additional defendant phase.

538
00:32:23,279 --> 00:32:24,039
That fast.

539
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:26,039
Mr. Xu,

540
00:32:26,039 --> 00:32:27,200
it must be very late there.

541
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,160
Still working?

542
00:32:28,960 --> 00:32:30,480
Insomnia. I'm used to it.

543
00:32:32,599 --> 00:32:33,400
I called
just to ask if,

544
00:32:34,839 --> 00:32:36,079
coincidentally or not,

545
00:32:36,880 --> 00:32:38,160
you might know the defendant.

546
00:32:39,519 --> 00:32:40,240
What?

547
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:44,119
She's an alum from your department.

548
00:32:44,559 --> 00:32:45,400
Two years behind.

549
00:32:45,839 --> 00:32:46,839
From my college?

550
00:32:47,880 --> 00:32:48,480
Yes.

551
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:50,319
Her name is Cen Sisi.

552
00:32:50,960 --> 00:32:51,799
Does that ring a bell?

553
00:32:59,640 --> 00:33:00,440
I'm with her now,
having dessert.

554
00:33:03,839 --> 00:33:05,720
It seems like the online smearing

555
00:33:05,880 --> 00:33:06,799
and today's encounter

556
00:33:07,480 --> 00:33:08,559
might not be coincidental.

557
00:33:27,200 --> 00:33:28,880
An open secret in the online lit scene.

558
00:33:29,119 --> 00:33:30,279
Steal a rookie's stories

559
00:33:30,480 --> 00:33:31,680
and concepts, then throw some money

560
00:33:32,079 --> 00:33:33,720
at them to shut them up.

561
00:33:34,480 --> 00:33:35,759
This fake statement...

562
00:33:36,079 --> 00:33:37,000
Does Lily Vale really think

563
00:33:37,000 --> 00:33:38,039
netizens are that stupid?

564
00:33:39,279 --> 00:33:40,680
A whole year without writing,

565
00:33:40,720 --> 00:33:41,920
is it her block,

566
00:33:41,920 --> 00:33:43,240
or nothing left to copy?

567
00:33:43,759 --> 00:33:44,880
Did she really write

568
00:33:44,880 --> 00:33:46,400
those past works herself?

569
00:33:50,759 --> 00:33:52,640
Are you okay?

570
00:33:53,400 --> 00:33:54,079
What's wrong?

571
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:55,440
Are you feeling unwell?

572
00:33:55,440 --> 00:33:56,960
You look off.

573
00:33:59,759 --> 00:34:00,519
Senior.

574
00:34:01,279 --> 00:34:02,119
What's wrong?

575
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:03,400
Are you okay?

576
00:34:06,480 --> 00:34:07,279
Sisi,

577
00:34:08,000 --> 00:34:09,320
Are you Su Cheng

578
00:34:09,320 --> 00:34:10,599
from Qianhe?

579
00:34:15,199 --> 00:34:15,719
What...

